title Canvas — API client & response types

class CanvasService {
  - baseUrl: string
  + getCourses(token, enrollmentState?): Promise<CanvasCourse[]>
  + getEnrollments(token, courseId?): Promise<CanvasEnrollment[]>
  + getAssignments(token, courseId): Promise<CanvasAssignment[]>
  + getAnnouncements(token, courses, count?): Promise<Array<CanvasAnnouncement & { course_name: string }>>
  + getSubmissions(token, courseId): Promise<CanvasSubmission[]>
  + getCalendarEvents(token, courseIds, start?, end?): Promise<CanvasCalendarEvent[]>
  + getConversations(token): Promise<CanvasConversation[]>
  + getConversationMessages(token, id): Promise<CanvasConversationDetail>
  - get<T>(url, token): Promise<T>
}

note right of CanvasService
  Every call adds Authorization: Bearer + User-Agent.
  Private get<T>() delegates to fetchJson().
  getConversations() calls fetchAllPages() directly.
  baseUrl: fhict.instructure.com (configurable).
end note

together {
  interface CanvasCourse {
    + id: number
    + name: string
    + course_code: string
    + created_at: string
    + start_at: string | null
    + end_at: string | null
    + enrollments?: Array<{ type: string; computed_current_score: number|null; computed_current_grade: string|null }>
  }

  interface CanvasAssignment {
    + id: number
    + name: string
    + due_at: string | null
    + points_possible: number | null
    + submission_types: string[]
    + description: string | null
    + rubric?: CanvasRubricCriterion[]
  }

  interface CanvasSubmission {
    + assignment_id: number
    + course_id?: number
    + attempt: number | null
    + score: number | null
    + grade: string | null
    + workflow_state?: string
    + submitted_at: string | null
    + graded_at: string | null
    + submission_comments?: Array<{ comment: string; author_name: string }>
    + rubric_assessment?: Record<string, { points: number; description?: string }>
    + assignment?: CanvasAssignment
  }
}

interface CanvasRubricCriterion {
  + id: string
  + description: string
  + ratings: Array<{ id: string; points: number; description: string }>
}

together {
  interface CanvasEnrollment {
    + course_id: number
    + course?: { name: string; course_code: string }
    + grades?: { current_score: number | null; current_grade: string | null }
    + last_activity_at: string | null
  }

  interface CanvasAnnouncement {
    + id: number
    + title: string
    + posted_at: string
    + author: { display_name: string } | null
    + message: string
    + html_url: string
  }
}

together {
  interface CanvasCalendarEvent {
    + id: number
    + title: string
    + start_at: string
    + end_at: string | null
    + description: string | null
    + html_url: string
    + context_code: string
    + type: string
  }

  interface CanvasConversation {
    + id: number
    + subject: string
    + last_message: string
    + last_message_at: string
    + message_count: number
    + workflow_state: string
    + context_name: string | null
    + participants: Array<{ name: string }>
  }
}

interface CanvasConversationDetail {
  + messages: Array<{ body: string; author_id: number; created_at: string }>
}

CanvasEnrollment    -[hidden]right-> CanvasAnnouncement
CanvasCalendarEvent -[hidden]right-> CanvasConversation

' ── cross-diagram stubs (defined in 01-common) ──────────────
class HttpUtil <<ref: common>>
class ConfigService <<ref: NestJS>>
class CanvasAuthError <<ref: common>>
class CanvasRateLimitError <<ref: common>>

CanvasCourse           -[hidden]right-> CanvasAssignment
CanvasAssignment       -[hidden]right-> CanvasSubmission

CanvasService *--> ConfigService          : config
CanvasService ..> HttpUtil                : fetchJson / fetchAllPages
CanvasService ..> CanvasCourse            : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasAssignment        : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasSubmission        : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasEnrollment        : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasAnnouncement      : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasCalendarEvent     : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasConversation      : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasConversationDetail : returns
CanvasService ..> CanvasAuthError         : <<throws>> (403)
CanvasService ..> CanvasRateLimitError    : <<throws>> (429)

CanvasAssignment ..> CanvasRubricCriterion  : rubric[]
CanvasSubmission ..> CanvasAssignment : assignment?

note right of CanvasSubmission
  workflow_state: "submitted" | "graded"
  | "pending_review" | "unsubmitted"
  rubric_assessment keyed by criterion id.
end note

@enduml
